ing: 1 (1 pound) fresh strawberries, hulled and cored
1 (7 ounce) can whipped cream (such as Reddi-WhipÂ®)
des: "Tried this at a country music festival and loved it! Easy, a little messy, but oh so worth it! Eat whole, all at once. This will seem like quite the mouthful, but will taste amazing! Enjoy."
ins: Pour amaretto liqueur into each strawberry and top with whipped cream.
